en_134610_0	Prime Minister Ranil Wickramasinghe says that a modern education system is scheduled to be introduced to Sri Lanka within next two years.
en_134610_1	The Premier made this remark at a function held in Newstead College, Negombo in celebration of its 200 th anniversary.
en_134610_2	The Premier also noted that the current curriculums should be changed and amended to go on par with world trends.
